NAME: Ratchet & Clank
DESC: Ratchet & Clank is a platformer-shooter video game developed by Insomniac Games. It is a re-imagining of the first game in the series, based on the film adaptation.

NAME: Tom Clancy's The Division
DESC: Tom Clancy's The Division is an online-only open world third-person shooter video game developed by Ubisoft.

NAME: Dark Souls III
DESC: Dark Souls III is an action role-playing video game developed by FromSoftware. It is the fourth entry in the Souls series.

NAME: Battleborn
DESC: Battleborn is an online first-person shooter video game developed by Gearbox Software.

NAME: MLB The Show 16
DESC: MLB The Show 16 is a Major League Baseball video game developed by Sony San Diego. It is the eleventh entry of the MLB: The Show franchise.

NAME: Halo 5: Guardians
DESC: Halo 5: Guardians is a first-person shooter video game developed by 343 Industries.

NAME: Call of Duty: Black Ops III
DESC: Call of Duty: Black Ops III is a military science fiction first-person shooter video game developed by Treyarch. It is the twelfth entry in the Call of Duty series.

NAME: Minecraft
DESC: Minecraft is a sandbox video game originally created by Swedish programmer Markus 'Notch' Persson and later developed and published by Mojang.

NAME: Star Wars Battlefront
DESC: Star Wars Battlefront is an action shooter video game developed by EA DICE. It is the third major release in the Star Wars: Battlefront sub-series.

NAME: Fallout 4
DESC: Fallout 4 is an action role-playing video game developed by Bethesda Game Studios. It is the fifth major installment in the Fallout series.

NAME: Star Fox Zero
DESC: Star Fox Zero is a 3D scrolling shooter video game developed by Nintendo and PlatinumGames. It is the sixth installment in the Star Fox series.

NAME: Super Smash Bros.
DESC: Super Smash Bros. is a fighting video game developed by Sora Ltd. It is the fourth installment in the Super Smash Bros. series of games.

NAME: Pokkén Tournament
DESC: Pokkén Tournament is an arcade fighting game developed by Bandai Namco Studios.

NAME: Super Mario Maker
DESC: Super Mario Maker is a side-scrolling platform video game and game creation system developed by Nintendo.

NAME: Mario Kart 8
DESC: Mario Kart 8 is a kart racing game developed by Nintendo. It is the eighth major installment in the Mario Kart series.

NAME: Hyrule Warriors Legends
DESC: Hyrule Warriors Legends is a hack-and-slash action video game developed by Omega Force and Team Ninja.

NAME: Bravely Second: End Layer
DESC: Bravely Second: End Layer is a Japanese role-playing video game developed by Silicon Studio. It is the sequel to Bravely Default.

NAME: Pokemon X
DESC: Pokémon X is a role-playing video game developed by Game Freak. It is one of the first installments in the sixth generation of the Pokémon series of role-playing games.

NAME: Final Fantasy Explorers
DESC: Final Fantasy Explorers is an action role-playing video game featuring classic Final Fantasy monsters and summons.

NAME: Animal Crossing: New Leaf
DESC: Animal Crossing: New Leaf is a life simulation video game. It is the fourth main title in Nintendo's Animal Crossing series.
